---
title: Lemon Dill Chicken & Couscous Bowls with Tomato Salad, Garlicky Yogurt Sauce & Almonds
description: Bowls are way past “having a moment.” They’ve become a pillar of our lunches and dinners. Why? It’s simple: everything’s better in a bowl! And the customizable combo of carbs, protein, veggies, and a drizzle of delicious sauce cannot be denied. This bright rendition is fully loaded. Hearty Israeli couscous with crunchy almonds and dill is topped with garlicky chicken, a fresh tomato salad, and a lemony, creamy sauce. One bite will have you totally bowled over.
